OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOrkney will
OL,6,Fhave a dry evening and night with
OL,7,Fclear periods. Rather cloudy across
OL,8,FShetland with occasional rain,
OL,9,Fbecoming drier later. Fresh
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds easing down.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA few brighter spells at
OL,13,Ffirst otherwise a rather cloudy day
OL,14,Fwith a few showers, becoming drier
OL,15,Flater in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
