OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA
OL,6,Fchangeable westerly pattern brings
OL,7,Fscattered showers or some longer
OL,8,Fspells of rain at times during this
OL,9,Fperiod. Variable cloud with some
OL,10,Fsunshine at times but often windy.
